title: 38. Real Talk: Everything Is A Test
itunes:title: 38. Real Talk: Everything Is A Test
description: Whether you like it or not, from the second you wake up...to the time you go to bed, you are constantly faced with temptations that ultimately shape your character and affect your future success. On today's show, Andy teaches you one simple shift in your perspective to build self-control.
